|| Precious Ngaceng Obisoso<ref>{{citeweb|url=https://www.instagram.com/p/B7Je9R-h22R/?igshid=s273gl5mzet|title=Miss International Nigeria 2020|accessdate=November 26, 2019}}</ref>||24||[[Sokoto]]\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|South Africa}} '''[[South Africa]]'''\n|[[Tamaryn Green]]\n|25\n|[[Paarl]]\n|-\n|'''{{flagicon|URU}} [[Miss Uruguay|Uruguay]] || Betina Jantan Margni Vilas||22||[[Montevideo]]\n|}\n\n==Upcoming national pageants==\nSeveral national pageants have been rescheduled due to [[2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic]] for further notice.\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"font-size: 95%;\"\n|-\n!Country\n!Date\n|-\n|'''{{flag|Sierra Leone}}'''\n| April 17, 2020<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://missosology.info/forum/viewtopic.php?f=0&t=1825434/|title=Face of Sierra Leone 2020|publisher=Missosology|access-date=15 March 2020}}</ref> \n|-\n|'''{{flag|Slovakia}}'''\n| April 25, 2020\n|-\n|'''{{flag|Czech Republic}}'''\n| May 3, 2020\n|-\n|'''{{flag|Panama}}'''\n| May 16, 2020<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/senoritapanama/|title=\u00a1Ya es oficial! La mujer m\u00e1s bella de Panam\u00e1 ser\u00e1 elegida la noche del 16 de mayo \"En Directo\", en Telemetro. El Se\u00f1orita Panam\u00e1 2020 regresa firme y con nuevos atractivos para sus seguidores|access-date=26 January 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|'''{{flag|Venezuela}}''' \n| May 21, 2020<ref>{{citeweb|url=https://www.el-carabobeno.com/el-miss-venezuela-2020-ya-tiene-sus-24-candidatas-oficiales/|title=El Miss Venezuela 2020 ya tiene sus 24 candidatas oficiales|publisher=el-carabobeno|access-date=2 March 2020}}</ref> \n|-\n|'''{{flag|Finland}}''' \n| May 22, 2020<ref>{{citeweb|url=https://www.ksml.fi/sjl/Nyt-voi-hakea-Miss-Suomi-kisaan-%E2%80%93-Valintaprosessista-tehd%C3%A4%C3%A4n-tv-ohjelma/1486140|title= Nyt voi hakea Miss Suomi -kisaan \u2013 Valintaprosessista tehd\u00e4\u00e4n tv-ohjelma| publisher=KSML|language=Finnish|date=20 December 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| '''{{flag|Philippines}}'''\n| May 31, 2020<ref>{{cite web|u