mmons category|Samsung Gear VR}}\n* {{official website}}\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20140906045517/http://www.samsungmobilepress.com/2014/09/03/Samsung-Explores-the-World-of-Mobile-Virtual-Reality-with-Gear-VR-1 Samsung Press Release]\n*[http://www.oculusvr.com/blog/introducing-the-samsung-gear-vr-innovator-edition/ Oculus Press Release]\n\n{{Mixed reality}}\n{{Samsung Gear}}\n{{portal bar|Technology}}\n\n[[Category:Mixed reality]]\n[[Category:Oculus VR]]\n[[Category:Products introduced in 2015]]\n[[Category:Samsung wearable devices]]\n[[Category:Virtual reality headsets]]\n[[Category:Samsung Gear VR]]\n", "name_user": "DannyS712", "label": "safe", "comment": "Fixing the location of periods / full stops", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Samsung_Gear_VR"}
